{
    "419:0": "5 pracalaparivartaḥ pañcamaḥ|",
    "419:1": "iti hi bhikṣavo bodhisattvastāṃ mahatīṃ devaparṣadamanayā dharmyayā kathayā saṃdarśya samādāpya samuttejya saṃpraharṣya kṣamāpayitvā maṅgalyāṃ devaparṣadamāmantrayate sma-gamiṣyāmyahaṃ mārṣā jambudvīpam|",
    "419:2": "mayā pūrvabodhisattvacaryāṃ caratā sattvāścaturbhiḥ saṃgrahavastubhirnimantritā dānena priyavadyenārthakriyayā samānārthatayā ca|",
    "419:3": "tadayuktametanmārṣā mama bhavedakṛtajñatā ca,",
    "419:4": "yadahamanuttarāyāṃ samyaksaṃbodhau nābhisaṃbuddheyam||",
    "419:5": "atha te tuṣitakāyikā devaputrā rudanto bodhisattvasya caraṇau parigṛhyaivamāhuḥ-idaṃ khalu satpuruṣa tuṣitabhavanaṃ tvayā vihīnaṃ na bhrājiṣyate|",
    "419:6": "atha bodhisattvastāṃ mahatī devaparṣadamevamāha-ayaṃ maitreyo bodhisattvo yuṣmākaṃ dharmaṃ deśayiṣyati|",
    "419:7": "atha bodhisattvaḥ svakācchirasaḥ paṭṭamaulaṃ cāvatārya maitreyasya bodhisattvasya śirasi pratiṣṭhāpayāmāsa|",
    "419:8": "evaṃ cāvocat-mamāntareṇa tvaṃ satpuruṣa anuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisaṃbhotsyase||",
    "419:9": "atha bodhisattvo maitreyaṃ bodhisattvaṃ tuṣitabhavane'bhiniṣadya punarapi tāṃ mahatīṃ devaparṣadamāmantrayate sma-kīdṛśenāhaṃ mārṣā rūpeṇa mātuḥ kukṣāvavakrāmeyam?",
    "419:10": "tatra kecidāhuḥ-mārṣā mānavakarūpeṇa|",
    "419:11": "kecidāhuḥ-śakrarūpeṇa|",
    "419:12": "kecidāhuḥ-brahmarūpeṇa|",
    "419:13": "kecidāhuḥ-mahārājikarūpeṇa|",
    "419:14": "kecidāhuḥ-vaiśravaṇarūpeṇa|",
    "419:15": "kecidāhuḥ-gandharvarūpeṇa|",
    "419:16": "kecidāhuḥ-kinnararūpeṇa|",
    "419:17": "kecidāhuḥ-mahoragarūpeṇa|",
    "419:18": "kecidāhuḥ-maheśvararūpeṇa|",
    "419:19": "kecidāhuḥ-candrarūpeṇa|",
    "419:20": "kecidāhuḥ-sūryarūpeṇa|",
    "419:21": "kecidāhuḥ-garuḍarūpeṇa|",
    "419:22": "tatrogratejo nāma brahmakāyiko devaputraḥ pūrvarṣijanmacyuto'vaivartiko'nuttarāyāḥ samyaksaṃbodheḥ,",
    "419:23": "sa evamāha-yathā brāhmaṇānāṃ mantravedaśāstrapāṭheṣvāgacchati,",
    "419:24": "tādṛśenaiva rūpeṇa bodhisattvo mātuḥ kukṣāvavakrāmitavyaḥ|",
    "419:25": "tatpunaḥ kīdṛśam?",
    "419:26": "gajavaramahāpramāṇaḥ ṣaḍdanto hemajālasaṃkāśaḥ suruciraḥ suraktaśīrṣaḥ sphuṭitagalitarūpavān|",
    "419:27": "etacchrutvā rūpaṃ brāhmaṇavedaśāstratattvajño vyākarṣitaśca|",
    "419:28": "ito vai bhāvī dvātriṃśallakṣaṇopetaḥ||",
    "419:29": "iti hi bhikṣavo bodhisattvo janmakālamavalokya tuṣitavarabhavanasthaḥ evaṃ rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhavare aṣṭau pūrvanimittānyupadarśayati sma|",
    "419:30": "katamānyaṣṭau?",
    "419:31": "tadyathā-vyapagatatṛṇakhāṇukaṇṭakaśarkarakaḍhalyanirmalaṃ suṣiktaṃ suśodhitamanākulavātatamorajovigatadaṃśakamakṣikāpataṅgasarīsṛpāpagatamavakīrṇakusumaṃ samaṃ pāṇitalajātaṃ tadgṛhaṃ saṃsthitamabhūt|",
    "419:32": "idaṃ prathamaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:33": "ye ca himavatparvatarājanivāsinaḥ patraguptaśukasārikākokilahaṃsakroñcamayūracakravākakuṇālakalaviṅkajīvaṃjīvakādayo vicitrarucirapakṣā manojñapriyabhāṣiṇaḥ śakunigaṇāḥ,",
    "419:34": "te āgatya rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhavare vitardiniryūhatoraṇagavākṣaharmyakūṭāgāraprāsādataleṣu sthitvā pramuditāḥ prītisaumanasyajātāḥ svakasvakāni rutānyudāharanti sma|",
    "419:35": "iti dvitīyaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:36": "ye ca rājñaḥ śuddhodanasyārāmaramaṇīyeṣu vanaramaṇīyeṣu codyānaramaṇīyeṣu nānāpuṣpaphalavṛkṣānānartukārikāḥ,",
    "419:37": "te sarve saṃpuṣpitāḥ saṃkusumitā abhūvan|",
    "419:38": "idaṃ tṛtīyaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:39": "yāśca rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya puṣkariṇyo jalaparibhogyasthāḥ,",
    "419:40": "tāḥ sarvāḥ śakaṭacakrapramāṇairanekakoṭīniyutaśatasahasrapatraiḥ padmaiḥ saṃchāditā abhūvan|",
    "419:41": "idaṃ caturthaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:42": "ye ca rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhavare bhājanaviṣaye sarpistailamadhuphāṇitaśarkarādyānāṃ te paribhujyamānāḥ kṣayaṃ na gacchanti sma|",
    "419:43": "paripūrṇā eva saṃdṛśyante sma|",
    "419:44": "idaṃ pañcamaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādūrabhūt||",
    "419:45": "ye ca rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhavarapradhāne mahatyantaḥpure bherīmṛdaṅgapaṇavatūṇavavīṇāveṇuvallakīsaṃpatāḍaprabhṛtayastūryabhāṇḍāḥ,",
    "419:46": "te sarve svayamaghaṭṭitā eva manojñaśabdaṃ muñcanti sma|",
    "419:47": "idaṃ ṣaṣṭhaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:48": "yāni ca rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhavarapradhāne suvarṇarūpyamaṇimuktāvaidūryaśaṅkhaśilāpravālādīnāṃ ratnānāṃ bhājanāni,",
    "419:49": "tāni sarvāṇi niravaśeṣaṃ vivṛtavimalaviśuddhaparipūrṇānyevaṃ virocante sma|",
    "419:50": "idaṃ saptamaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt||",
    "419:51": "vimalaviśuddhayā candrasūryajihmīkaraṇayā prabhayā kāyacittodbilyasaṃjananyā tadgṛhaṃ samantādavabhāsitamabhūt|",
    "419:52": "idamaṣṭamaṃ pūrvanimittaṃ prādurabhūt|",
    "419:53": "māyā ca devī snātānuliptagātrā vividhābharaṇaviṣkambhitabhujā suślakṣṇasulīlavastravaradhāriṇī prītiprāmodyaprasādapratilabdhā sārdhaṃ daśabhiḥ strīsahasraiḥ parivṛtā puraskṛtā rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya saṃgītiprāsāde sukhopaviṣṭasyāntikamupasaṃkramya dakṣiṇe pārśve ratnajālapratyupte bhadrāsane niṣadya smitamukhī vyapagatabhṛkuṭikā prahasitavadanā rājānaṃ śuddhodanamābhirgāthābhirabhāṣat—",
    "419:54": "sādho śṛṇuṣva mama pārthiva bhūmipālā",
    "419:55": "yācāmi te nṛpatiradya varaṃ prayaccha|",
    "419:56": "abhiprāyu mahya yatha cittamanaḥpraharṣaṃ",
    "419:57": "tanme śṛṇuṣva bhava prītamanā udagraḥ||1||",
    "419:58": "gṛhṇāmi deva vrataśīlavaropavāsaṃ",
    "419:59": "aṣṭāṅgapoṣadhamahaṃ jagi maitracittā|",
    "419:60": "prāṇeṣu hiṃsaviratā sada śuddhabhāvā",
    "419:61": "premaṃ yathātmani pareṣu tathā karomi||2||",
    "419:62": "stainyādvivarjitamanā madalobhahīnā",
    "419:63": "kāmeṣu mithya nṛpate na samācariṣye|",
    "419:64": "satye sthitā apiśunā paruṣaprahīṇā",
    "419:65": "saṃdhipralāpamaśubhaṃ na samācariṣye||3||",
    "419:66": "vyāpādadoṣakhilamohamadaprahīṇā",
    "419:67": "sarvā abhidhya vigatā svadhanena tuṣṭā|",
    "419:68": "samyakprayukta akuhānilayā anirṣyu",
    "419:69": "karmā yathā daśa ime kuśalā cariṣye||4||",
    "419:70": "mā tvaṃ narendra mayi kāmatṛṣāṃ kuruṣva",
    "419:71": "śīlavrateṣvabhiratāya susaṃvṛtāya|",
    "419:72": "mā te apuṇya nṛpate bhavi dīrgharātra-",
    "419:73": "manumodayā hi mama śīlavratopavāsam||5||",
    "419:74": "chando mameṣa nṛpate praviśādya śīghraṃ",
    "419:75": "prāsādaharmyaśikhare sthita dhārtarāṣṭre|",
    "419:76": "sakhibhiḥ sadā parivṛtā sukha modayeyaṃ",
    "419:77": "puṣpābhikīrṇaśayane mṛduke sugandhe||6||",
    "419:78": "na ca kāñcukīya puruṣā na pi dārakāśca",
    "419:79": "na ca istri prākṛta mamā purataḥ sthiheyā|",
    "419:80": "no cāmanāpa mama rūpa na śabdagandhān",
    "419:81": "nānyatra iṣṭamadhurā śṛṇuyā suśabdān||7||",
    "419:82": "ye rodhabandhanagatāḥ parimuñca sarvān",
    "419:83": "dravyāmbarāśca puruṣāndhaninaḥ kuruṣva|",
    "419:84": "vastrānnapāna rathayugya tathāśvayānaṃ",
    "419:85": "dada saptarātrikamidaṃ jagataḥ sukhārtham||8||",
    "419:86": "no co vivādakalahā na ca roṣavākyā",
    "419:87": "cānyonyamaitramanaso hitasaumyacittā|",
    "419:88": "asmin pure puruṣa iṣṭika dārakāśca",
    "419:89": "devāśca nandanagatā sahitā ramantām||9||",
    "419:90": "na ca rājadaṇḍanabhaṭā na tathā kudaṇḍā",
    "419:91": "notpīḍanā na pi ca tarjanatāḍanā vā|",
    "419:92": "sarvān prasannamanaso hitamaitracitta",
    "419:93": "vīkṣasva deva janatāṃ yatha ekaputram||10||",
    "419:94": "śrutvaiva rāja vacanaṃ paramaṃ udagraṃ",
    "419:95": "prāhāstu sarvamidameva yathā tavecchā|",
    "419:96": "abhiprāyu tubhya manasā svanucintitāni",
    "419:97": "yadyācase tava varaṃ tadahaṃ dadāmi||11||",
    "419:98": "ājñāpyaḥ pārthivavaraḥ svakapāriṣadyāṃ",
    "419:99": "prāsādaśreṣṭhaśikhare prakarotha ṛddhim|",
    "419:100": "puṣpābhikīrṇaruciraṃ varadhūpagandhaṃ",
    "419:101": "chatrāpatākasamalaṃkṛtatālapaṃktim||12||",
    "419:102": "viṃśatsahasra raṇaśoṇḍa vicitravarmāṃ",
    "419:103": "nārācaśūlaśaraśaktigṛhītakhaṅgāḥ|",
    "419:104": "parivārayātha dhṛtarājyamanojñaghoṣaṃ",
    "419:105": "devyā'bhayārtha karuṇāsthita rakṣamāṇā||13||",
    "419:106": "strībhistu sā parivṛtā yatha devakanyā",
    "419:107": "snātānuliptapravarāmbarabhūṣitāṅgī|",
    "419:108": "tūryaiḥ sahasramanugītamanojñaghoṣaiḥ",
    "419:109": "āruhya devyupaviveśa marutsnuṣeva||14||",
    "419:110": "divyairmahārthasuvicitrasuratnapādaiḥ",
    "419:111": "svāstīrṇapuṣpavividhaiḥ śayane manojñe|",
    "419:112": "śayane sthitā vigalitā maṇiratnacūḍā",
    "419:113": "yatha miśrakāvanagatā khalu devakanyā||15||",
    "419:114": "atha khalu bhikṣavaścatvāro mahārājānaḥ śakraśca devānāmindraḥ suyāmaśca devaputraḥ saṃtuṣitaśca sunirmitaśca paranirmitavaśavartī ca sārthavāhaśca māraputrabrahmā ca sahāṃpatirbrahmottaraśca purohitaḥ subrahmā ca purohitaḥ prabhāvyūhābhāsvaraśca maheśvaraśca śuddhāvāsakāyikā niṣṭhāgataścākaniṣṭhaśca etāni cānyāni cānekāni devaśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatya anyonyamevāhuḥ-ayuktametanmārṣā asmākaṃ syādakṛtajñatā ca,",
    "419:115": "yadvayamekākinamadvitīyaṃ bodhisattvamutsṛjema|",
    "419:116": "ko'smākaṃ mārṣā utsahate bodhisattvaṃ satatasamitamanubaddhumavakramaṇagarbhasthānajanmayauvanabhūmidārakakrīḍāntaḥpuranā-ṭakasaṃdarśanābhiniṣkramaṇaduṣkaracaryābodhimaṇḍopasaṃkramaṇamāradharṣaṇabodhyabhisaṃbodhana-dharmacakrapravartanaṃ yāvanmahāparinirvāṇāddhitacittatayā snigdhacittatayā priyacittatayā maitracittatayā saumyacittatayā?",
    "419:117": "tasyāṃ velāyāmimāṃ gāthāmabhāṣata—",
    "419:118": "ko votsaheta vararūpadharam",
    "419:119": "anubandhayituṃ satataṃ prītamanāḥ|",
    "419:120": "kaḥ puṇyateja yaśasā vacasā",
    "419:121": "svayamātmanecchati vibaddhayitum||16||",
    "419:122": "yasyepsitaṃ tridaśadevapure",
    "419:123": "divyaiḥ sukhairhi ramituṃ satatam|",
    "419:124": "paramāpsarobhiriha kāmaguṇaiḥ",
    "419:125": "anubaddhitāṃ vimalacandramukham||17||",
    "419:126": "tatha miśrake vanavare rucire",
    "419:127": "divyākare ramitu devapure|",
    "419:128": "puṣpotkare kanakacūrṇanime",
    "419:129": "anubandhatāṃ vimalatejadharam||18||",
    "419:130": "yasyepsitaṃ ramituḥ citrarathe",
    "419:131": "tatha nandane suravadhūsahitaḥ|",
    "419:132": "māndāravaiḥ kusumapatracite",
    "419:133": "anubandhatāmimu mahāpuruṣam||19||",
    "419:134": "yāmādhipatyamatha vā tuṣitai-",
    "419:135": "ratha vāpi prārthayati ceśvaratām|",
    "419:136": "pūjāraho bhavitu sarvajage",
    "419:137": "anubandhatāmimu anantayaśam||20||",
    "419:138": "yo icchati nirmitapure rucire",
    "419:139": "vaśavartidevabhavane ramitum|",
    "419:140": "manasaiva sarvamanubhoktikriyā",
    "419:141": "anubandhatāmimu guṇāgradharam||21||",
    "419:142": "māreśvaro na ca praduṣṭamanā",
    "419:143": "sarvavidhaiśvaryapāragataḥ|",
    "419:144": "kāmeśvaro vaśitapāragato",
    "419:145": "gacchatvasau hitakareṇa saha||22||",
    "419:146": "tatha kāmadhātu samatikramituṃ",
    "419:147": "mati yasya brahmapuramāvasitum|",
    "419:148": "caturapramāṇaprabhatejadharaḥ",
    "419:149": "so'dyānubaddhatu mahāpuruṣam||23||",
    "419:150": "atha vāpi yasya manujeṣu mati",
    "419:151": "varacakravartiviṣaye vipule|",
    "419:152": "ratnākaramabhayasaukhyadadam",
    "419:153": "anubandhatāṃ vipulapuṇyadharam||24||",
    "419:154": "pṛthivīśvarastatha pi śreṣṭhisuto",
    "419:155": "āḍhyo mahādhanu mahānicayaḥ|",
    "419:156": "parivāravānnihataśatrugaṇo",
    "419:157": "gacchatvasau hitakareṇa saha||25||",
    "419:158": "rūpaṃ ca bhogamapi ceśvaratā",
    "419:159": "kīrtiryaśaśca balatā guṇavatī|",
    "419:160": "ādeyavākya bhavi grāhyaruto",
    "419:161": "brahmeśvaraṃ samupayātu vidum||26||",
    "419:162": "ye divya kāma tatha mānuṣakāṃ",
    "419:163": "yo icchatī tribhavi sarvasukham|",
    "419:164": "dhyāne sukhaṃ ca pravivekasukhaṃ",
    "419:165": "dharmeśvaraṃ samanubandhayatām||27||",
    "419:166": "rāgaprahāṇu tatha doṣamapī",
    "419:167": "yo icchate tatha kileśajaham|",
    "419:168": "śānta praśānta upaśāntamanā",
    "419:169": "so dāntacittamanuyātu laghum||28||",
    "419:170": "śaikṣā aśaikṣa tatha pratyekajinā",
    "419:171": "sarvajñajñānamanuprāpuritum|",
    "419:172": "daśabhirbalairnaditu siṃha iva",
    "419:173": "guṇasāgaraṃ samanuyātu vidum||29||",
    "419:174": "pithituṃ apāyapatha yeṣa matir",
    "419:175": "vivṛtuṃ ca ṣaṅgatipathaṃ hyamṛtam|",
    "419:176": "aṣṭāṅgamārgagamanena gatim",
    "419:177": "anubandhatāṃ gatipathāntakaram||30||",
    "419:178": "yo icchate sugata pūjayituṃ",
    "419:179": "dharmaṃ ca teṣu śrutikāruṇike|",
    "419:180": "prāpto guṇānapi ca saṃghagatān",
    "419:181": "guṇasāgaraṃ samanuyātu imam||31||",
    "419:182": "jātijarāmaraṇaduḥkhakṣaye",
    "419:183": "saṃsārabandhana vimokṣayitum|",
    "419:184": "carituṃ viśuddhagamanāntasamaṃ",
    "419:185": "so śuddhasattvamanubandhayatām||32||",
    "419:186": "iṣṭo manāpa priyu sarvajage",
    "419:187": "varalakṣaṇo varaguṇopacitaḥ|",
    "419:188": "ātmā paraṃ ca tatha mocayituṃ",
    "419:189": "priyadarśanaṃ samupayātu vidum||33||",
    "419:190": "śīlaṃ samādhi tatha prajñamayī",
    "419:191": "gambhīradurdaśaduropagamam|",
    "419:192": "yo icchate vidu vimukti labhe",
    "419:193": "so vaidyarājamanuyātu laghum||34||",
    "419:194": "ete ca anya guṇa naikavidhā",
    "419:195": "upapatti saukhya tatha nirvṛtiye|",
    "419:196": "sarvairguṇebhi pratipūrṇa siddhaye",
    "419:197": "siddhavrataṃ samanuyātu vidum||35|| iti||",
    "419:198": "idaṃ khalu vacanaṃ śrutvā caturaśītisahasrāṇi cāturmahārājikānāṃ devānāṃ śatasahasraṃ trayatriṃśānāṃ śatasahasraṃ yāmānāṃ śatasahasraṃ tuṣitānāṃ śatasahasraṃ nirmāṇaratīnāṃ śatasahasraṃ paranirmitavaśavartīnāṃ devānāṃ ṣaṣṭisahasrāṇi mārakāyikānāṃ pūrvaśubhakarmaniryātānāṃ aṣṭaṣaṣṭisahasrāṇi brahmakāyikānāṃ bahūni śatasahasrāṇi yāvadakaniṣṭhānāṃ devānāṃ saṃnipatitānyabhūvan|",
    "419:199": "anye ca bhūyaḥ pūrvadakṣiṇapaścimottarebhyo digbhyo bahūni devaśatasahasrāṇi saṃnipatitānyabhūvan|",
    "419:200": "tebhyo ye udāratamā devaputrāste tāṃ mahatīṃ devaparṣadaṃ gāthābhirabhyabhāṣantaḥ—",
    "419:201": "hanta śṛṇotha vacanaṃ amareśvarāho",
    "419:202": "asmin vidhānamati yādṛśatatvabhūtā|",
    "419:203": "tyaktārthikāmarati dhyānasukhaṃ praṇītam",
    "419:204": "anubandhayāma imamuttamaśuddhasattvam||36||",
    "419:205": "okrāntapāda tatha garbhasthitaṃ mahātmaṃ",
    "419:206": "pūjārahaṃ atiśayamabhipūjayāmaḥ|",
    "419:207": "puṇyaiḥ surakṣitamṛṣiṃ parirakṣisanto",
    "419:208": "yasyāvatāra labhate na manaḥ praduṣṭam||37||",
    "419:209": "saṃgītitūryaracitaiśca suvādyakaiśca",
    "419:210": "varṇāguṇāṃ kathayato guṇasāgarasya|",
    "419:211": "kurvāma devamanujāna praharṣaṇīyaṃ",
    "419:212": "yaṃ śrutva bodhivaracitta jane janeryā||38||",
    "419:213": "puṣpābhikīrṇa nṛpateśca karoma gehaṃ",
    "419:214": "kālāgurūttamasudhūpitasaumyagandham|",
    "419:215": "yaṃ ghrātva devamanujāśca bhavantyudagrā",
    "419:216": "vigatajvarāśca sukhinaśca bhavantyarogāḥ||39||",
    "419:217": "māndāravaiśca kusumaistatha pārijātai-",
    "419:218": "ścandraiḥ sucandra tatha sthālavirocamānaiḥ|",
    "419:219": "puṣpābhikīrṇa kapilāhvaya taṃ karoma",
    "419:220": "pūjārtha pūrvaśubhakarmasamudgatasya||40||",
    "419:221": "yāvacca garbhi vasate trimalairalipto",
    "419:222": "yāvajjarāmaraṇa cāntakaraḥ prasūtaḥ|",
    "419:223": "tāvatprasannamanaso anubandhayāma",
    "419:224": "eṣā matirmatidharasya karoma pūjām||41||",
    "419:225": "lābhā sulabdha vipulāḥ suramānuṣāṇāṃ",
    "419:226": "drakṣyanti jānu imu saptapadāṃ kramantam|",
    "419:227": "śakraiśca brahmaṇakaraiḥ parigṛhyamānaṃ",
    "419:228": "gandhodakaiḥ snapiyamāni suśuddhasattvam||42||",
    "419:229": "yāvacca loki anuvartanatāṃ karoti",
    "419:230": "antaḥpure vasati kāmakileśaghātī|",
    "419:231": "yāvacca niṣkramati rājyamapāsya sarvaṃ",
    "419:232": "tāvatprasannamanaso anubandhayāmaḥ||43||",
    "419:233": "yāvadupaiti mahimaṇḍi tṛṇāṃ gṛhītvā",
    "419:234": "yāvacca bodhi spṛśate vinihatya māram|",
    "419:235": "adhyeṣṭu brāhmaṇayutebhi pravarti cakraṃ",
    "419:236": "tāvatkaroma vipulāṃ sugatasya pūjām||44||",
    "419:237": "yada buddhakāryu kṛtu bheṣyati trisahasre",
    "419:238": "sattvāna koṭinayutā amṛte vinītā|",
    "419:239": "nirvāṇamārgamupayāsyati śītibhāvaṃ",
    "419:240": "tāvanmahāśayamṛṣiṃ na jahāma sarve||45||iti||",
    "419:241": "atha khalu bhikṣavaḥ kāmadhātvīśvarāṇāṃ devakanyānāṃ bodhisattvasya rūpakāyapariniṣpattiṃ dṛṣṭvā etadabhavat-kīdṛśī tvasau kanyā bhaviṣyati yā imaṃ varapravaraśuddhasattvaṃ dhārayiṣyati|",
    "419:242": "tāḥ kautūhalajātā varapravarapuṣpadhūpadīpagandhamālyavilepanacūrṇacīvaraparigṛhītā divyamanomayātmabhāvapratilabdhāḥ puṇyavipākādhisthānādhisthitāḥ tasmin kṣaṇe'marapurabhavanādantarhitāḥ kapilāhvaye mahāpuravare udyānaśatasahasraparimaṇḍite rājñaḥ śuddhodanasya gṛhe dhṛtarāṣṭre mahāprāsāde amarabhavanaprakāśe vigalitāmbaradhāriṇyaḥ śubhavimalatejapratimaṇḍitā divyābharaṇastambhitabhujāḥ śayanavaragatāṃ māyādevīmekāṅgulikayopadarśayantyo gaganatalagatāḥ parasparaṃ gāthābhirabhyabhāṣanta—",
    "419:243": "amarapuragatāna apsarāṇāṃ",
    "419:244": "rūpa manorama dṛṣṭva bodhisattve|",
    "419:245": "matiriyamabhavattadā hi tāsāṃ",
    "419:246": "pramada nu kīdṛśa bodhisattvamātā||46||",
    "419:247": "tāśca sahitapuṣpamālyahastā",
    "419:248": "upagami veśma nṛpasya jātakāṅkṣā|",
    "419:249": "puṣpa tatha vilepanāṃ gṛhītvā",
    "419:250": "daśanakhaañjalibhirnamasyamānāḥ||47||",
    "419:251": "vigalitavasanāḥ salīlarūpāḥ",
    "419:252": "karatala dakṣiṇi aṅgulīṃ praṇamya|",
    "419:253": "śayanagata vidarśi māyadevīṃ",
    "419:254": "sādhu nirīkṣatha rūpa mānuṣīṇām||48||",
    "419:255": "vayamiha abhimanyayāma anye",
    "419:256": "paramamanorama surūpa apsarāṇām|",
    "419:257": "ima nṛpativadhūṃ nirīkṣamāṇā",
    "419:258": "jihma vipaśyatha divya ātmabhāvām||49||",
    "419:259": "ratiriva sadṛśī guṇānvitā ca",
    "419:260": "jananiriyaṃ pravarāgrapudgalasya|",
    "419:261": "maṇiratana yathā subhājanastha",
    "419:262": "tatha iva bhājana devi devadeve||50||",
    "419:263": "karacaraṇatalebhi yāvadūrdhvaṃ",
    "419:264": "aṅga mahorama divya ātirekāḥ|",
    "419:265": "prekṣatu nayanānna cāsti tṛptiṃ",
    "419:266": "bhūya praharṣati citta mānasaṃ ca||51||",
    "419:267": "śaśiriva gagane virājate'syā",
    "419:268": "vadanu varaṃ ca virāja gātrabhāsā|",
    "419:269": "raviriva vimalā śaśīva dīptā",
    "419:270": "tatha prabha niścarate'sya ātmabhāvāt||52||",
    "419:271": "kanakamiva sujātajātarūpā",
    "419:272": "varṇa virocati deviye tathaiva|",
    "419:273": "bhramaravaranikāśa kuntalānī",
    "419:274": "mṛdukasugandhaśravāsya mūrdhajāni||53||",
    "419:275": "kamaladalanibhe tathāsya netre",
    "419:276": "daśanaviśuddha nabheva jyotiṣāṇi|",
    "419:277": "cāpa iva tanūdarī viśālā",
    "419:278": "pārśva samudgata māṃsi nāsti saṃdhiḥ||54||",
    "419:279": "gajabhujasadṛśe'sya ūrujaṅghe",
    "419:280": "jānu sujātvanupūrvamudgatāsya|",
    "419:281": "karatalacaraṇā samā suraktā",
    "419:282": "vyaktamiyaṃ khalu devakanya nānyā||55||",
    "419:283": "eva bahuvidhaṃ nirīkṣya devīṃ",
    "419:284": "kusuma kṣipitva pradakṣiṇaṃ ca kṛtvā|",
    "419:285": "supiya yaśavatī jinasya mātā",
    "419:286": "punarapi devapuraṃ gatā kṣaṇena||56||",
    "419:287": "atha caturi caturdiśāsu pālāḥ",
    "419:288": "śakra suyāma tathaiva nirmitāśca|",
    "419:289": "devagaṇa kumbhāṇḍa rākṣasāśca",
    "419:290": "asura mahoraga kinnarāśca vocan||57||",
    "419:291": "gacchata purato narottamasya",
    "419:292": "puruṣavarasya karotha rakṣaguptim|",
    "419:293": "mā kuruta jage manaḥpradoṣaṃ",
    "419:294": "mā ca karota viheṭha mānuṣāṇām||58||",
    "419:295": "yatra gṛhavarasmi māyadevī",
    "419:296": "tatra samagra sapāriṣadya sarve|",
    "419:297": "asidhanuśaraśaktikhaṅgahastā",
    "419:298": "gaganatalasmi sthitā nirīkṣayātha||59||",
    "419:299": "jñātva cyavanakāla devaputrā",
    "419:300": "upagami māyasakāśa hṛṣṭacittā|",
    "419:301": "puṣpa tatha vilepanāṃ gṛhītvā",
    "419:302": "daśanakhaañjalibhirnamasyamānāḥ||60||",
    "419:303": "cyava cyava hi narendra śuddhasattvā",
    "419:304": "ayu samayo bhavato'dya vādisiṃha|",
    "419:305": "kṛpakaruṇa janitva sarvaloke",
    "419:306": "asmi adhyeṣama dharmadānahetoḥ||61|| iti ||",
    "419:307": "atha khalu bhikṣavo bodhisattvasya cyavanakālasamaye pūrvasyā diśo bahūni bodhisattvaśatasahasrāṇi sarva ekajātipratibaddhāstuṣitavarabhavanavāsino yena bodhisattvastenopasaṃkrāman bodhisattvasya pūjākarmaṇe|",
    "419:308": "evaṃ daśabhyo digbhyo ekaikasyā diśo bahūni bodhisattvaśatasahasrāṇi sarva ekajātipratibaddhāstuṣitavarabhavanavāsino yena bodhisattvastenopasaṃkrāman bodhisattvasya pūjākarmaṇe|",
    "419:309": "cāturmahārājakāyikebhyo devebhyaścaturaśītyapsaraḥśatasahasrāṇyevaṃ trayatriṃśato yāmebhyastuṣitebhyo nirmāṇaratibhyaḥ paranirmitavaśavartibhyo devebhyaścaturaśītyapsaraḥ-śatasahasrāṇi nānātūryasaṃgītivāditena yena bodhisattvastenopasaṃkrāman bodhisattvasya pūjākarmaṇe||",
    "419:310": "atha khalu bodhisattvaḥ śrīgarbhasiṃhāsane sarvapuṇyasamudgate sarvadevanāgasaṃdarśane mahākūṭāgāre niṣadya sārdhaṃ bodhisattvairdevanāgayakṣakoṭiniyutaśatasahasraiḥ parivṛtaḥ puraskṛtastuṣitavarabhavanāt pracalati sma|",
    "419:311": "pracalatā ca bhikṣavo bodhisattvena tathārūpā kāyāt prabhā muktābhūd yayā prabhayā ayaṃ trisāhasramahāsāhasro lokadhāturevaṃ vipulavistīrṇo mahatodāreṇa supracalitapūrveṇa divyaprabhāsamatikrāntenāvabhāsena parisphuṭo'bhūt|",
    "419:312": "yā api tā lokāntarikā aghā aghasphuṭā andhakārāstamisrā yatremau candrasūryāvevaṃ maharddhikāvevaṃ mahānubhāvāvevaṃ maheśākhyau ābhayā ābhāṃ varṇena varṇaṃ tejasā tejo nābhitapato nābhivirocataḥ,",
    "419:313": "tatra ye sattvā upapannāste svakānapi bāhuprasāritānna paśyanti|",
    "419:314": "tathāpi tasmin samaye mahata udārasyāvabhāsasya prādurbhāvo'bhūt|",
    "419:315": "ye ca tatra sattvā upapannāste tenaivāvabhāsena sphuṭāḥ samānā anyonyaṃ samyak paśyanti sma|",
    "419:316": "anyonyaṃ saṃjānante sma|",
    "419:317": "evaṃ cāhuḥ- anye'pi kila bhoḥ sattvā ihopapannāḥ kila bho iti||",
    "419:318": "ayaṃ ca trisāhasramahāsāhasro lokadhātuḥ ṣaḍvikāramaṣṭādaśamahānimittamabhūt|",
    "419:319": "akampat prākampat saṃprākampat|",
    "419:320": "avedhat prāvedhat saṃprāvedhat|",
    "419:321": "acalat prācalat saṃprācalat|",
    "419:322": "akṣubhyat prākṣubhyat saṃprākṣubhyat|",
    "419:323": "araṇat prāraṇat saṃprāraṇat|",
    "419:324": "agarjat prāgarjat saṃprāgarjat|",
    "419:325": "ante'vanamati sma,",
    "419:326": "madhye unnamati sma|",
    "419:327": "madhye'vanamati sma,",
    "419:328": "ante unnamati sma|",
    "419:329": "pūrvasyāṃ diśyavanamati sma,",
    "419:330": "paścimāyāṃ diśyunnamati sma|",
    "419:331": "paścimāyāṃ diśyavanamati sma,",
    "419:332": "pūrvasyāṃ diśyunnamati sma|",
    "419:333": "dakṣiṇasyāṃ diśyavanamati sma,",
    "419:334": "uttarasyāṃ diśyunnamati sma|",
    "419:335": "uttarasyāṃ diśyavanamati sma,",
    "419:336": "dakṣiṇasyāṃ diśyunnamati sma|",
    "419:337": "tasmin samaye harṣaṇīyāstoṣaṇīyāḥ premaṇīyāḥ prasādanīyā avalokanīyāḥ prahlādanīyā nirvarṇanīyā asecanīyā apratikūlā anuttrāsakarāḥ śabdāḥ śrūyante sma|",
    "419:338": "na ca kasyacit sattvasya tasmin kṣaṇe viheṭhā vā trāso vā bhayaṃ vā stambhitatvaṃ vābhūt|",
    "419:339": "na ca bhūyaḥ sūryācandramasorna brahmaśakralokapālānāṃ tasmin kṣaṇe prabhā prajñāyate sma|",
    "419:340": "sarvanarakatiryagyoniyamalokopapannāśca sattvāstasmin kṣaṇe vigataduḥkhā abhūvan sarvasukhasamarpitāḥ|",
    "419:341": "na ca kasyacit sattvasya rāgo bādhate sma,",
    "419:342": "dveṣo vā moho vā,",
    "419:343": "īrṣyā vā mātsaryaṃ vā,",
    "419:344": "māno vā mrakṣo vā,",
    "419:345": "mado vā krodho vā,",
    "419:346": "vyāpādo vā paridāho vā|",
    "419:347": "sarvasattvāstasmin kṣaṇe maitracittā hitacittāḥ parasparaṃ mātāpitṛsaṅgino'bhūvan|",
    "419:348": "aghaṭṭitāni ca divyamānuṣyakāṇi tūryakoṭiniyutaśatasahasrāṇi manojñaghoṣamutsṛjanti sma|",
    "419:349": "devakoṭīnayutaśatasahasrāṇi pāṇibhiraṃsaiḥ śirobhistaṃ mahāvimānaṃ vahanti sma|",
    "419:350": "tāni cāpsaraḥśatasahasrāṇi svāṃ svāṃ saṃgītiṃ saṃprayujya purataḥ pṛṣṭhato vāmadakṣiṇena ca sthitvā bodhisattvaṃ saṃgītirutasvareṇābhistuvanti sma—",
    "419:351": "pūrvakarmaśubhasaṃcitasya te",
    "419:352": "dīrgharātrakuśaloditasya te|",
    "419:353": "satyadharmanayaśodhitasya te",
    "419:354": "pūja adya vipulā pravartate||62||",
    "419:355": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:356": "dānu dattu priyaputradhītarā|",
    "419:357": "tasya dānacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:358": "yena divya kusumāḥ pravarṣitāḥ||63||",
    "419:359": "ātmamāṃsa tulayitva te vibho",
    "419:360": "so'bhidattu priyapakṣikāraṇāt|",
    "419:361": "tasya dānacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:362": "pretaloki labhi pānabhojanam||64||",
    "419:363": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:364": "śīla rakṣitamakhaṇḍanavratam|",
    "419:365": "tasya śīlacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:366": "yena akṣaṇa apāya śodhitāḥ||65||",
    "419:367": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:368": "kṣānti bhāvita nidānabodhaye|",
    "419:369": "tasya kṣānticaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:370": "maitracitta bhuta devamānuṣāḥ||66||",
    "419:371": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:372": "vīryu bhāvitamalīnamuttamam|",
    "419:373": "tasya vīryacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:374": "yena kāyu yatha meru śobhate||67||",
    "419:375": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:376": "dhyāna dhyāyita kileśadhyeṣaṇāt|",
    "419:377": "tasya dhyānacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:378": "yena kleśa jagato na bādhate||68||",
    "419:379": "pūrvi tubhya bahukalpakoṭiyo",
    "419:380": "prajña bhāvita kileśachedanī|",
    "419:381": "tasya prajñacaritasya tatphalaṃ",
    "419:382": "yena ābha paramā virocate|| 69||",
    "419:383": "maitravarmita kileśasūdanā",
    "419:384": "sarvasattvakaruṇāya udgatā|",
    "419:385": "modiprāpta paramā upekṣakā",
    "419:386": "brahmabhūta sugatā namo'stu te||70||",
    "419:387": "prajña ulkaprabha tejasodgatā",
    "419:388": "sarvadoṣatamamohaśodhakā|",
    "419:389": "cakṣubhūta trisahasrināyakā",
    "419:390": "mārgadeśika mune namo'stu te||71||",
    "419:391": "ṛddhipādavarabhijñakovidā",
    "419:392": "satyadarśi paramārthi śikṣitā|",
    "419:393": "tīrṇa tārayasi anyaprāṇino",
    "419:394": "dāśabhūta sugatā namo'stu te||72||",
    "419:395": "sarvopāyavarabhijñakovidā",
    "419:396": "darśayasi cyutimacyuticyutim|",
    "419:397": "lokadharmabhavanābhivartase",
    "419:398": "no ca loki kvaci opalipyase||73||",
    "419:399": "lābha teṣa paramā acintiyā",
    "419:400": "yeṣu darśana śravaṃ ca eṣyase|",
    "419:401": "kiṃ punaḥ śṛṇuya yo tidharmatāṃ",
    "419:402": "śraddha prīti vipulā janeṣyase||74||",
    "419:403": "jihma sarva tuṣitālayo bhuto",
    "419:404": "jambudvīpi puri yo udāgataḥ|",
    "419:405": "prāṇikoṭinayutā acintiyāṃ",
    "419:406": "bodhayiṣyasi prasupta kleśato||75||",
    "419:407": "ṛddha sphīta puramadya bheṣyatī",
    "419:408": "devakoṭinayutaiḥ samākulam|",
    "419:409": "apsarobhi turiyairnināditaṃ",
    "419:410": "rājagehi madhuraṃ śruṇiṣyati||76||",
    "419:411": "puṇyatejabharitā śubhakarmaṇā",
    "419:412": "nāri sā paramarūpaupetā|",
    "419:413": "yasya putra ayameva samṛddhaḥ",
    "419:414": "tisraloki abhibhāti śīriye||77||",
    "419:415": "no bhuyo puravarasmi dehināṃ",
    "419:416": "lobhadoṣakalahā vivādakā|",
    "419:417": "sarva maitramanasaḥ sagauravā",
    "419:418": "bhāvino naravarasya tejasā||78||",
    "419:419": "rājavaṃśa nṛpateḥ pravardhate",
    "419:420": "cakravartikularājasaṃbhavaḥ|",
    "419:421": "bheṣyate kapilasāhvayaṃ puraṃ",
    "419:422": "ratnakoṣabharitaṃ susamṛddham||79||",
    "419:423": "yakṣarākṣasakumbhāṇḍaguhyakā",
    "419:424": "devadānavagaṇāḥ saindrakāḥ|",
    "419:425": "ye sthitā naravarasya rakṣakāḥ",
    "419:426": "teṣu mokṣa nacireṇa bheṣyate||80||",
    "419:427": "puṇyupārjitu stavitva nāyakaṃ",
    "419:428": "premagauravamupasthapisva nā|",
    "419:429": "sarva bodhi pariṇāmayāmahe",
    "419:430": "kṣipra bhoma yatha tvaṃ narottama||81|| iti||",
    "419:431": "iti śrīlalitavistare pracalaparivarto nāma pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ||"
}